            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p2">每日你点击无数次连结，每一个连结背后连到不同互联网内容，但世界上透过网页入侵电脑、手机的陷阱多如星屑，稍一不慎你很容易会随时跌入黑客、骗徒陷阱，信用卡、帐户资料随时被盗。被黑客窃取 Facebook、WhatsApp 帐户的个人、商户要取回帐户，是非常麻烦的一件事，信用卡被盗刷更是难于追讨。如何可以得到更周全的保护，上网可以更加安心？除了 VPN 之外，你还需要一个<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">周全的网络安全服务</a>。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195608 aligncenter" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-580x580.jpg 580w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-900x900.jpg 900w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-120x120.jpg 120w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-768x768.jpg 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">避开有害软件（Malware）入侵电脑、网路</h2><p class="p2">VPN 服务可以协助你避开黑客、骗徒的陷阱。目前最常令用户遭受损失的是网路上流传的有害软件（Malware）。有害软件包括了电脑／手机病毒、蠕虫、木马、勒索软件、广告软件等。这些有害软件可在你的内部网络上散布更多间谍软件、勒索软件，更会消耗公司网络的频宽，更甚者会删除公司网络上电脑的档案，为公司网络打开大门，给黑客随意入侵。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-1280x731.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-768x439.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-1536x877.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">最常避免有害软件的方法，就是在电脑安装防毒软件，随时用 Windows Update、Mac 系统更新功能更新你的电脑堵塞网络漏洞，不要随便打开不明人士传送给你的连结、文件，以至图片，也不要实行不知名网站提供的档案。有时电邮模仿大企业官方格式，需要你开启档案，不仅开启就可能会中招。</p><p class="p2">你还可利用 VPN 协助你避开有害软件。<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark CleanWeb Adblock VPN</a> 就可为你隔绝网路上的有害软件、让你避免点击入有害的连结后中招。万一你点击了这些连结，VPN 会向你作出提示连结可能有安全风险，让用户再三确认，可避免很多一 click 即中招的情况。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-1280x731.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-768x439.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-1536x877.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p2">避开钓鱼攻击泄漏你的信用卡、帐户资料</h2><p class="p2">钓鱼攻击是一个用户很易中招，泄漏信用卡、银行帐户资料的渠道。不法份子透过一个设计与银行、信用卡网站非常类似的网站介面，并以不同方式诱骗用户输入个人资料。万一用户输入了自己的个人资料，资料会马上被黑客获取，并进行盗用、非法活动。</p><p class="p2">要避免受到钓鱼攻击，最好的方法就是自己上网时小心留意，不要随便在电邮提供的网址中登入自己的帐户。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-1280x730.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-768x438.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-1536x876.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2"><a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark CleanWeb</a> 就可协助你阻挡网路上的钓鱼攻击。此功能结合 Adblock 可阻挡网路上已被标签为钓鱼攻击的网站、连结，让用户远离钓鱼攻击的威胁。</p><h2 class="p2">避免企业伺服器「注入攻击」</h2><p class="p2">「注入攻击」是企业伺服器最经常面对的网路安全风险之一。黑客透过 SQL 隐码 (SQL injection) 攻击，将有害程式码注入企业伺服器的资料库中，可引致资料库数据面临被删除、更改、泄漏的危机。至于另一种更危险的攻击方式叫「跨网站指令码」（Cross-site scripting），黑客会将有害程式码注入企业网站的程式码中，其他使用者在观看网页时便会受到影响，这对企业形象带来不可估计的破坏。</p><p class="p2">很多时企业即使被黑客入侵，除非受到重大安全影响，否则也不会向用户通报，多数都暪天过海，最终用户会承担帐户资料被盗风险。虽然 VPN 服务并不能防护，但 Surfshark 用户可同时使用该公司提供的 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark Alert</a>，你存放于企业伺服器的帐户资料，即使被黑客盗取，<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark Alert</a> 可感应到这类意外，当你的帐户资料出现于市面上黑客贩售的数据库中，可即时向你通报，让你及早实行对应措施，包括更改密码、删除帐户等。</p><h2 class="p2">DNS 快取污染</h2><p class="p2">用户连接网络服务，其实背后都要靠一个「DNS」伺服器，将网址的文字，转化成为连接到企业伺服器的网址。如果这个 DNS 快取受到污染，你将不能连到企业官方网站，反而会连到黑客所操踪的网站。作为一个小用户，你可以使用 VPN 服务来检测 DNS 快取污染的发生，避免落入黑客的圈套。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195605 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">要安全防护，避免不同种类的入侵</h2><p class="p2">VPN 可以为你提供网路连线安全保障，上网数据不受黑客窃听。而为了避免其他网络陷阱，用户可留意 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark One</a> 最周全的网络安全服务。此服务包括有 Surfshark VPN、Surfshark Antivirus 防毒软件、Surfshark Search 提供安全搜寻结果、Surfshark Alert 在你的帐户资料万一在黑客市场流通都可马上向你通报。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195606 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">unwire 读者优惠</h2><p class="p2">现在只要通过这条 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark One 连结</a>进入官方网站，订阅两年就可即时享有 84% 优惠 + 2 个月免费，只需要 HK$23.02 一个月，就可以获取上述提到的 Surfshark One 安全服务套餐。另外也可以选择订阅一年，优惠则是 77%。限时优惠，读者们不要错过。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195607 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-694x396.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-694x396.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-1280x731.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-768x439.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-1536x877.jpg 1536w